### Project Structure
/project-root
├── cmd/           # Main entry points (CLI commands)
├── pkg/
│   ├── api/       # NetBox API client
│   ├── discovery/ # Network & service discovery modules
│   ├── mapping/   # Topology mapping logic
│   ├── models/    # Data structures for devices, services, etc.
│   └── utils/     # Utility functions
├── configs/       # Configuration files
├── docs/          # Documentation
└── main.go
